All Classes

Class Description
Bishop
The class Bishop represents a bishop chess piece.
Cell
The class Cell is a representation of a square on the chess board.
Chess
The class Chess is the main class of the program and is used to play a game of chess.
Color
The enum Color represents the possible colors used in a chess game for pieces and squares on the board.
King
The class King represents a king chess piece
Knight
The class Knight represents a knight chess piece.
Logic
The class Logic contains methods used during a game of chess such as mapping file-rank to array indices, identifying player input, checking for check and checkmate, etc...
Pawn
The class Pawn represents a pawn chess piece
Piece
The class Piece is a general representation of a chess piece.
Queen
The class Queen represents a queen chess piece.
Rook
The class Rook represents a rook chess piece.
Type
The enum Type represents the possible types of chess pieces.
